flowchart LR
    Driver([Driver App])
    Rider([Rider App])
    LocIngest[Location Ingest<br/>WebSocket]
    GeoCache[(Driver Geo Index<br/>Redis GEO,<br/>TTL 10s)]
    LocLog[(Location History<br/>partitioned stream)]
    Match[Matching Service<br/>geo query + score<br/>+ sequential offer]
    Trip[Trip Service<br/>FSM: requested -&gt; matched<br/>-&gt; on_trip -&gt; completed]
    Routing[Routing Service<br/>Maps + ETA]
    Pricing[Pricing Service<br/>surge per cell]
    Payment[Payment Service]

    Driver -.->|loc / 4s| LocIngest
    LocIngest --> GeoCache
    LocIngest -.-> LocLog
    Rider -->|request ride| Match
    Match --> GeoCache
    Match -.->|offer via WS| Driver
    Match -->|on accept| Trip
    Trip <--> Routing
    Trip <--> Pricing
    Trip --> Payment
    Trip -.->|status| Rider

    classDef external fill:#1e2533,stroke:#3a4a6e,color:#cfd6e6
    classDef service fill:#1a3a2e,stroke:#3a6e54,color:#cfe6d6
    classDef store fill:#1e2a3e,stroke:#3a5a8e,color:#cfdcef
    classDef config fill:#3a2e1a,stroke:#6e5a3a,color:#efdfcf

    class Driver,Rider external
    class LocIngest,Match,Trip,Routing,Pricing,Payment service
    class GeoCache,LocLog store
